---
title: Almond-Crusted Chicken with Sweet Potato Mash
description: Making crispy, almond- and panko-coated chicken is surprisingly easy when you follow our simple steps. The end result? Crunchy, savoury chicken served with a smooth maple sweet-potato mash and garlicky zucchini.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-en-croute-damandes-7c9ee8bc.jpg
